  <description>Seed by Seed is an independant game development studio, created to bring the coop game Pile Up to life. 

We were brought together by the love of shared breakfasts, cute plants surrounding us, and carefully handcrafted videogames. We want to share this love with others, and we have chosen to combine our talents to create soft, fun, friendly games, games that remind people why everybody loves to play with their loved ones.</description>

